      "module_path": "commands::task_contract",
      "docs": "Arguments for `sotp task-contract check`. layer: optional TDDD layer (domain, usecase, infrastructure, cli_driver, cli, or cli_composition) identifying the layer signal document to check; passed as an opaque CLI string validated as LayerId in the primary adapter; when omitted (None), all 6 canonical TDDD layers are iterated internally and their results combined. track_id: active track identifier (also opaque at this boundary); when omitted, auto-resolved from the current git branch (track/<id>). items_dir: path to the track items directory; defaults to 'track/items'.",
      "spec_refs": [
        { "file": "track/items/pre-review-task-contract-conformance-gate-2026-06-27/spec.json", "anchor": "IN-04" },
