      "docs": "Execute `sotp task-contract check`. Resolves track_id_opt (explicit track_id or auto from track/<id> branch), then delegates to task_contract_check_core. When no track id can be resolved, the core helper returns ExitCode::SUCCESS without invoking the composition root so CI passes gracefully on main or non-track branches. When Some, the core helper constructs a TaskContractCompositionRoot, calls task_contract_check(layer, track_id, items_dir), and converts the CommandOutcome to a process ExitCode (0 on Passed, non-zero on Blocked or error).",
